 ing debut writers to those who have already had a continuous and lasting i
 mpact on the literary landscape.\nThe 2026 Literary Awards will confer nea
 rly $350\,000 to writers and translators. Spanning fiction\, poetry\, essa
 y\, translation\, and more\, these books are dynamic\, diverse\, and thoug
 ht-provoking examples of literary excellence.\nGET TICKETS\nSee the finali
 sts\nCheck out the titles on Bookshop
